{"tid":2452202,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"時事台又有三隻白卡狗，一個踩港，一個cheap, 一個瘋狂屈藍","createTime":"2021-03-18T16:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T09:44:21.000Z","uid":34571,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"da1cdc26123b323534f0a31a6c55fc12a5980a5a","tid":2452202,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"會員：愛爾蘭共和軍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TWWMczp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTWWMczp.jpg&h=b9d241b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zWvQEdX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzWvQEdX.jpg&h=94873ee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D8zh3FP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD8zh3FP.jpg&h=0fd15ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nblame the victim, 話黃種人抵死，自己攞黎，比人打應該硬淨啲解釋自己唔係支那人，唔撐佢就係藍絲撐驚狗， 但成個post完全無人撐警，無藍絲，係基本用腦分析<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會員：想得太遠<br />\n台灣人食壽司塞晒啲飯係枱面，佢就話台灣人做衰野，都係香港人扮，香港人先會咁衰，踩港到痴線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gY5MW29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgY5MW29.jpg&h=626a8467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tvQpJJd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtvQpJJd.jpg&h=7315dffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會員：大師兄黎明<br />\n<br />\n大大聲話自己食手卷專登食淨啲飯，掉咗二十舊飯，壽司係專登塞飽顧客，係商店孤寒，唔比佢走飯，所以商店不仁佢不義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢好啱好正確<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ae9Fg38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fae9Fg38.jpg&h=9262c725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGOrcCu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGOrcCu.jpg&h=3c993b42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e19a08d7f7658a8047db160e33db97f8c00e710","tid":2452202,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB